name: Xawara
description: Xawara is the word for epidemic in Yanomami language, a tribal people that live in north Brazil and south Venezuela and has suffered with many diseases brought by white people and greedy gold miners. Images: Ary Man Guary. Actors: Carolina Zeferina, Luccas Barbosa and Cafa Sorridente. Script: Leonardo Maciel. Original soundtrack: Vitor Ço. Aditional sountrack (creative commons): MC Jakie - A mamãe chegou.
